org.coach.tracing.service.ntp
Class NtpHeader

java.lang.Object
  org.coach.tracing.service.ntp.NtpHeader

public class NtpHeader
extends java.lang.Object

This class encapsulates the header of a NtpDatagram. See rfc2030 for more details.
